column1: #bike description - a descriptive reference for the bike e.g. PT050
#weight - the bicycle mass in Kg with no decimal places e.g. 12

column2: park longitude - when a bike is parked
column3: the park latitude and longitude are given in decimal degrees e.g. 41.152712

column1: #max battery capacity - the battery max capacity in kWh e.g. 1
#actual battery capacity - the percentage with no decimal places of the battery capacity e.g. 75 for a battery with 0.75kWh charge
#aerodynamic coefficient - bicycle aerodynamic coefficient with 2 decimal places e.g. 1.10
#bicycle description;weight;type;park latitude;park longitude;max battery capacity;actual battery capacity;aerodynamic coefficient
